{"tid":2231730,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣西站21歲女與男友感情爭執　25歲男整爛手機涉兩宗罪被捕","createTime":"2020-10-06T01:07:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T11:21:58.000Z","uid":44209,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1842b4f57311d5a59a295ba301e206d1d895077f","tid":2231730,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T01:07:24.000Z","msg":"感情問題一律建議分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨日（5日）晚上8時許，警方接獲報案指，港鐵荃灣西站一名21歲姓郭女子，與其25歲姓陳男友因感情問題爭執，其間陳男懷疑曾以手毀壞郭的手提電話及手鏈。警方接報到場，經初步調查，陳男早前亦曾在元朗一單位內，出言語恐嚇女友，案件列作刑事恐嚇及刑事毀壞，陳男涉案被捕，案件交由荃灣警區刑事調查隊第四隊跟進。"},{"pid":"9083b235c3386099ab71867f9dcab387e40fabc9","tid":2231730,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T01:13:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"34f1b1d220abab75bc36dd5c8db0ce4c9088fcc7","tid":2231730,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T07:33:09.000Z","msg":"情困青年彌敦道墮樓 昏迷送院亡<br />\n<br />\n據了解，死者近日與女友分手，疑因受感情打擊而尋死。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201006/GRMASUKJGJE4BMSP5SUQ6AWONY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201006%2FGRMASUKJGJE4BMSP5SUQ6AWONY%2F&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZLwOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=b19b89a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201006%2FGRMASUKJGJE4BMSP5SUQ6AWONY%2F&h=24924f66\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201006/GRMASUKJGJE4BMSP5SUQ6AWONY/</a>"},{"pid":"e2ddfa79fc36b5434ffad1ecde3092b73b05b869","tid":2231730,"uid":121546,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T08:35:55.000Z","msg":"換轉係女人咁做實係口頭警告就算"},{"pid":"72670045dd914371207d52f112243d14d2e47aad","tid":2231730,"uid":261172,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e2ddfa79fc36b5434ffad1ecde3092b73b05b869","tid":2231730,"uid":121546,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T08:35:55.000